  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:26:14.473050+00:00",
  "text": "teleport can't display popup  in SSR when disabled prop is false value.\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/likuner/nuxt-ssr-template.git\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\nsee my repo [nuxt-ssr-template](https://github.com/likuner/nuxt-ssr-template.git) for detail, it uses el-tooltip from element-plus as a demo.\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\n\r\nCan display the pop-up normally.\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\n\r\nCan't display the pop-up normally.\r\n\r\n### System Info\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Any additional comments?\r\n\r\n_No response_",
